  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc7 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba9 - \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Disturbing events overnight in Galle - New Zealand",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "New Zealand High Commissioner Michael Appleton expressed concern over the overnight events in Galle.",
        "On the morning of the 27th, the three forces removed the people who were peacefully protesting in front of the Presidential Secretariat located in the Gallimugattidal area of \u200b\u200bColombo.",
        "Following this, New Zealand High Commissioner Michael Appleton expressed concern and condemnation on his official Twitter page.",
        "\u201cThe events that took place overnight in Galle are alarming. Freedom of speech, freedom of the media and the right to peaceful protest are the foundations of all free societies. So they should be protected, New Zealand High Commissioner Michael Appleton said."
      ],
